{"tid":2161420,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"泛民一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「泛民，你又想一直當議員了！」","createTime":"2020-08-17T14:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T23:29:45.000Z","uid":26846,"like":45,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d0af816470a1863c95fbb0149c06ca58df859af6","tid":2161420,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"泛民一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「泛民，你又想一直當議員了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「兄弟爬山，堅守議會戰線。」便排出十萬港元。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又戀棧議員權位了！」泛民睜大眼睛說，「議會需要反對聲音，守住議會&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼守住？早陣子你才偷懶缺席，惡法差幾票反對然後就通過了。」泛民便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「缺席不能算贊成&hellip;&hellip;棄權！&hellip;&hellip;議員的事，能算贊成麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「不分化」，什麼「五毛」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"385d8d25af92641f2f22c77bdc71500cb35a2fc0","tid":2161420,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12357d458cbfbf77c463a7702561671afbcd9f03","tid":2161420,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd161259be211dac52c684f5777d116b03ab214","tid":2161420,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇笑點既"},{"pid":"bfc84045f12930ba9739f4aa4aeb550bc5d657a2","tid":2161420,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d564ad1f0ea02fcda25961be23d6317a7e0140","tid":2161420,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaab179390ee359e881b0d5ef2d36f87b